Package: MetaNet
Type: Package
Title: Network analysis for large omics data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Peng Chen [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Peng Chen <pengchen2001@zju.edu.cn>
Authors@R:
    person("Peng", "Chen",email ="pengchen2001@zju.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Comprehensive network analysis package.
    Calculate correlation network fastly, accelerate lots of analysis by parallel computing.
    Support for multi-omics data, search sub-nets fluently.
    Handle bigger data, more than 10,000 nodes in each omics.
    Offer various layout method for multi-omics network and some interfaces to other software (Gephi, Cytoscape, ggplot), easy to visualize.
    Provide comprehensive topology indexes calculationï¼Œincluding ecological network stability.
